{# Template: bug-hunt/bug-hunt-convergence-check.j2 #}
{# goal: Compute normalized convergence metric for bug-hunt cycles. #}

[inference]
temperature = 0.1
reasoning_effort = "medium"
verbosity = "terse"
max_tokens = 1000
thinking_budget = "standard"

Given bug-hunt findings, compute convergence where 0 means no unresolved critical/high-confidence bug blockers remain in this cycle.

Input:
```json
{{ primary_result | tojson }}
```

Return JSON only:
```json
{
  "convergence_metric": 0.0,
  "rationale": "short explanation",
  "blockers": []
}
```
